node.text: What a year it’s been - pandemic, Beirut explosions, George Floyd, Brianna Taylor, and so much more. If you reading this, you are one of the fortunate ones who made it. Thanks for following, for the support and encouragement. Wishing you a better year ahead, please stay safe and healthy, sending you lots of love, Tracey xxx PS - sound comes and goes, sorry, let’s blame it on 2020 🤷🏻‍♀️😂❤️

node.text: Hats off to @phillipshouse for this incredible initiative- donate $25 to a charity of your choice corresponding to the global pandemic, and they will give you a gift! node.text: I CHOOSE YOU… AND YOU AND YOU!!! A stunning selection of @novelcollection diamond rings - richly saturated and beautifully set. node.text: SAPPHIRES OR RUBIES??? 💙❤️ @extraitajewelry are preparing for Las Vegas and one of my favorite Italian jewelry brands, @picchiotti_fine_jewellery , will be exhibiting! Here I am wearing two different @picchiotti_fine_jewellery necklaces - one with sapphires and the other with rubies. This is the craftsmanship I’ve come to associate with #TheExtraordinaryItalianJewelry - visit @extraitajewelry for a full list of Italian exhibitors at both @by_couture and @jckevents 🇮🇹 ❤️💎💙🇮🇹❤️💎💙🇮🇹 #thediamondsgirl #thediamondsgirlxpicchiotti #picchiottifinejewellery #italianstyle #italianjewelry #cdxita #jewelry #sapphire #ruby #diamond #statementjewelry

node.text: WHY WEAR YOUR HEART ON YOUR SLEEVE WHEN YOU CAN WEAR IT ON YOUR FINGER??? 💕 @aarachminov_diamonds really rocked my world with this heart shape diamond, isn’t it a beauty? Love seeing those beautiful facets at the back, and then… pure perfection as it faces the camera. One of the most challenging shapes to cut, but @aarachminov_diamonds do it to perfection as always! 💕💎👏🏻💎💥❤️💎 #thediamondsgirl #thediamondsgirlxaar #aarachminov #aarachminovdiamonds #diamond #diamonds #naturaldiamond #loosediamonds #heart #heartshape #love

node.text: Can’t begin to describe the incredible day I had today, thanks to @muzoemeralds ! Hopefully these pics will give you some insight - blown away by the beauty of Colombia and the warmth of the people. Massive thanks to George from @muzoemeralds for making this possible - you are a ROCK STAR! Tomorrow we will be in the @muzoemeralds Bogata offices, seeing the cutting, polishing, and setting of the spectacular Muzo emeralds! 💚💚💚 #thediamondsgirl #thediamondsgirlxmuzo #muzo #muzoemeralds #emerald #emeralds #colombia #gems #gemstone
